data.description: Welcome home to your new spacious 4 bedroom home. Second floor offers 4 bedrooms and 2 full baths. First floor you will find a large eat in kitchen w large pantry and a connecting dining room, A large office or sitting room connected to a large family room. Great for open entertaining.  First floor laundry and a half bath. You will also find a full finished basement with plenty of storage and a full bath with a stand up shower.
